<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Neutral" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Neutral,</orth> the same: <cit><quote>loyal and n. in a moment,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 115</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>which came from one that's of a n. heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.7.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 7, 48</bibl></cit>. Substantively: <cit><quote>like a n. to his will and matter,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.503" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 503</bibl></cit>.
